query:
SELECT r.id, r.requestNumber, r.currentStage, m.name as mosqueName, 
       (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM quotations q WHERE q.requestId = r.id) as quotationCount
FROM serviceRequests r 
LEFT JOIN mosques m ON r.mosqueId = m.id
ORDER BY quotationCount DESC
LIMIT 5;
